  "instructions": [
    "Combine peanuts, peanut oil, onion, garlic, ginger, and green chili in a bowl.",
    "Mix well to combine and set aside for 15 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Thread the peanut mixture onto skewers, leaving a small space between each peanut.",
    "Brush the skewers with soy sauce and honey, then sprinkle with garam masala and salt.",
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Grill the skewers for 5-7 minutes on each side, or until the peanuts are crispy and golden brown.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped cilantro.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Slice the skewers into individual portions if desired.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
